   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Arriving in the city of the Alexandrians, I learned that the most pious bishop had sailed away to Pelusium; therefore, will your Magnificence, with your customary grace (?), knowing the force of the decree, order that he be reminded with the others . . . . . from the Thebaid to find the matter ready, so that I too as usual may thank your magnificence and so that the dedicated men, as usual, may also themselves proclaim your greatness.</ab>
